<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: left;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative on {!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Dear {!Job_placement__c.Contact_Name__c},&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">I hope you have enjoyed your placement on NCS with The Challenge on one of our pilot programmes. &nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b>This payment email is regarding your work on NCS: Real Challenge Action. You will receive up to four emails in total, each corresponding to a specific NCS: Real Challenge Action day. &nbsp;</b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Your payment for completing the NCS: Real Challenge Action day on</font></div><div><font size="2"><font style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">on&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b>{!Job_placement__c.Assignment_start_date__c}<font color="#ff0000">&nbsp;</font></b><font face="arial">for</font></font><font color="#ff0000" style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</font><font><font face="arial">{!Job_placement__c.Wave__c}</font><font face="arial">&nbsp;</font></font><font style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">is outlined below.&nbsp;</font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font size="2"><font face="arial" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Your&nbsp;payment for the&nbsp;specified&nbsp;work date will be split into two payments.&nbsp;The standard gross pay for completing a full working day is&nbsp;</font></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Job_placement__c.Total_Amount_to_Pay__c}</span><font size="2"><font face="arial" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.&nbsp;</font><font face="arial" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">You will receive an initial payment of 70%&nbsp;of the gross pay for the&nbsp;specified&nbsp;NCS: Real Challenge Action day&nbsp;on&nbsp;</font><font face="arial">{!Job_placement__c.Advance_payment_date__c}<font face="Arial, sans-serif">. This payment is an advance and thus will not be subjected to Tax and National Insurance. You will receive {!Job_placement__c.Payroll_advance_owed__c} on this advance date.&nbsp;</font></font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">The remaining 30% gross pay for the&nbsp;specified&nbsp;NCS: Real Challenge Action day will be subject to Tax and National Insurance and will be received on&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c}.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">The overall amount which you receive on {!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c} will vary according to your tax code, but will be significantly smaller than your first payment for this role, and may be close to zero.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">On your payslip (sent via email on {!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c}) , you will see the total amount and breakdown of payment which you will receive for the entire wave.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px;">Due to new auto-enrolment legislation, employees of The Challenge, including summer staff, will be automatically enrolled in a workplace pension scheme. This is a way of saving for your retirement that's arranged by your employer. This affects staff who earn more than £473 per month and are aged between 22 and state pension age. You will see your pension contributions on your payslip. For further information, please go to&nbsp;<a href="http://www.gov.uk/workplace-pensions" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">www.gov.uk/workplace-<wbr>pensions</a>.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px;"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px;">Further communications</font><span style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, including how to opt out,</span><span style="font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;will be sent to you in September where we will start to process all summer staff for auto-enrolment. At that point, i</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">f you would like to opt out of the pension scheme, you will need an opt-out form from The People's Pension, which you can get from and then return to by emailing&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:thepeoplespension@bandce.co.uk" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">thepeoplespension@<wbr>bandce.co.uk</a><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 13.333333015441895px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Staff will have a one month opt-out period: this begins from the day the administration for their becoming a member is complete, i.e. one month from the date of enrolment, which will not take place until September.</span><font size="3" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">If you have any questions, do contact us.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Yours sincerely,&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">NCS with The Challenge</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">CR 4.1b</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">*NCS:&nbsp;</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Real&nbsp;Challenge&nbsp;Action refers to the last section of the programme. &nbsp; </font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div></div>]]></td>
